Source: etcd
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: community-pkgs <https://github.com/community-pkgs/packages>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.2
Homepage: https://etcd.io

Package: etcd
Architecture: any
Depends:
 adduser,
 ${misc:Depends},
Recommends: etcd-client
Description: Distributed reliable key-value store (server)
 etcd is a distributed, reliable key-value store for the most critical data
 of a distributed system. It is used as the backend storage for Kubernetes
 cluster state, service discovery, and distributed configuration.
 .
 This package contains the etcd server daemon.

Package: etcd-client
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Distributed reliable key-value store (client tools)
 etcd is a distributed, reliable key-value store for the most critical data
 of a distributed system.
 .
 This package contains etcdctl (the etcd CLI client) and etcdutl (the
 offline etcd utility tool).
